on this app, my employees often mistakely use the upload and download button.
for more data safety. 
Store last update timestampz of each stories.

when clicked,
  Upload: show the first confirmation. then check the cloud storylines data if:
    1. any of the storyline's last edit date is greater than local storylines
    2. any of the storyline's char length is greater than local storylines
  
  Download: show the first confirmation. then check the cloud storylines data if:
    1. any of the storyline's last edit date is less than local storylines
    2. any of the storyline's char length is less than local storylines

If any show the warnings with proper details and if they still proceed only then move forward
this way data loss will be more infrequent